aa(lp18
VWho is at risk? People like you.
p19
aVIt's not just the Africans that should be concerned about that.
p20
aVAll friends of Africa, that will have reason to be in Africa at some point in time,
p21
aVshould be very concerned about this deplorable situation.
p22
aVHas anyone here wondered what will happen
p23
aVif you go back to your room at night,
p24
aVand you start getting chest pains, shortness of breath, sweating?
p25
aVYou're having a heart attack. What are you going to do?
p26
aVWill you fly back to the U.S., Germany, Europe?
p27
aVNo, you will die. 50 percent will die within 24 hours, if not treated.
