aa(lp124
VWe made sure that we produced some things ourselves.
p125
aVWe do not buy unit doses of radiopharmaceuticals.
p126
aVWe get the generators from the companies.
p127
aVWe manufacture them in-house, ourselves. That keeps the costs down.
p128
aVSo, for a radiopharmaceutical in the U.S. \u2014
p129
aVthat you'll get a unit dose for 250 dollars \u2014
p130
aVwhen we're finished manufacturing it in-house,
p131
aVwe come at a price of about two dollars.
